{"tid":1502041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前一晚先講轉場既係咪on9 講野負責啦唔該","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:43:38.000Z","uid":97523,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42fb1c9be1e6a4b8d1379df338e8fe27cea126bf","tid":1502041,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n你地對唔對得住主辦方？<br />\n人地文宣做哂 印哂 準備好哂 <br />\n同埋荃葵青既街坊點諗？<br />\n佢地可能都籌備好耐<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n前一晚帶風向轉場只會分薄人流<br />\n咪撚同我講各有各做 兩邊都出<br />\n事實係一日兩場活動 兩邊都只會兩頭不到岸<br />\n人多就安全你估淨係口號黎？<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最撚重要既係一場活動係要時間宣傳 準備 籌劃<br />\n唔係連登開個post投個票咁簡單</span><br />\n824本身都睇唔過眼<br />\n分上下午活動係乜撚野玩法<br />\n到今晚又有批人想玩多次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機場係春袋大家都知<br />\n但咪撚玩爛張牌得唔得啊！！</span>"},{"pid":"5b70e4217cb053a467645779157692e26a0f289d","tid":1502041,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bff9444ac55d91658b41ba901c3521931e97f9ea","tid":1502041,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683ef6351d9c3cb3bc8fecd0a233de18ff450eba","tid":1502041,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"認同尤其係第一點"},{"pid":"b3e3f0d0d897b16c97c27b6807c92d03c9f3218e","tid":1502041,"uid":97523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"683ef6351d9c3cb3bc8fecd0a233de18ff450eba","tid":1502041,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"認同尤其係第一點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"主辦方籌備咗咁耐<br />\n有埋不反對<br />\n唔係留言打句紅字「825機場」就夠影響力嫁<br />\n講野負責啦"}]}